          "reviewBody": "Great School!\nMy kid is very happy to be in this School . Teachers are very nice , helpful and they are open minded ,think outside the box to make a successful educational experience for students. Teachers truly invested in my child's education and their growth as learner. More affordable than other private schools. I have never worried about my child as she is under their care and guidance .",
