            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Dehradun Public school is a wonderful school with an amazing staff and teachers! The teachers are really nurturing and caring and i loved the structure and support for the students. I really love this and my daughter is looking forward going to school everyday. It is really a safe and nurturing environment that really helps students to learn. The teachers really understands the students and support them. I also like the communication between the school teachers and parents. Even during the pandemic, Dehradun Public school has maintained the safety of kids while encouraging the highest standards of education!! Teachers are always trying to work with the kids here no matter the barrier or complications, they never give up on kids!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
