          },
          "reviewBody": "The teachers are exceptional and hardworking and greatly loved by me  and my classmates. I find them to be incredibly enthusiastic and I see them working with and guiding families and children who need extra help. They meet kids were they are and effectively work with learning differences to help them reach the next level. I could not be more impressed with the faculty. The administration is working smartly to give kids and families an outstanding elementary school experience. I am thrilled to be part of this school. *Thank you DDPS*",
          "publisher": {
